<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFRobertson1968">Robertson, Alan R. (November 1968). "<a href="http://www.opticsinfobase.org/abstract.cfm?URI=josa-58-11-1528" class="external text" title="http://www.opticsinfobase.org/abstract.cfm?URI=josa-58-11-1528" rel="nofollow">Computation of Correlated Color Temperature and Distribution Temperature</a>". <i><a href="/wiki/JOSA" title="JOSA">JOSA</a></i> <b>58</b> (11): 1528–1535<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.opticsinfobase.org/abstract.cfm?URI=josa-58-11-1528" class="external free" title="http://www.opticsinfobase.org/abstract.cfm?URI=josa-58-11-1528" rel="nofollow">http://www.opticsinfobase.org/abstract.cfm?URI=josa-58-11-1528</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Computation+of+Correlated+Color+Temperature+and+Distribution+Temperature&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BJOSA%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Robertson&amp;rft.aufirst=Alan+R.&amp;rft.au=Robertson%2C+Alan+R.&amp;rft.date=November+1968&amp;rft.volume=58&amp;rft.issue=11&amp;rft.pages=1528%E2%80%931535&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.opticsinfobase.org%2Fabstract.cfm%3FURI%3Djosa-58-11-1528&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Color_temperature"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
