<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWalter1992">Walter, Wolfgang (February 1992). "Determination of correlated color temperature based on a color-appearance model". <i>Color Research &amp; Application</i> <b>17</b> (1): 24–30. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002%2Fcol.5080170107" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002%2Fcol.5080170107" rel="nofollow">10.1002/col.5080170107</a></span>.  "The concept of correlated color temperature is only useful for lamps with chromaticity points close to the blackbody…".</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Determination+of+correlated+color+temperature+based+on+a+color-appearance+model&amp;rft.jtitle=Color+Research+%26+Application&amp;rft.aulast=Walter&amp;rft.aufirst=Wolfgang&amp;rft.au=Walter%2C+Wolfgang&amp;rft.date=February+1992&amp;rft.volume=17&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=24%E2%80%9330&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1002%2Fcol.5080170107&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Color_temperature"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-schanda-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-schanda_20-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFSchanda2007">Schanda, János (2007). "3: CIE Colorimetry". <i>Colorimetry: Understanding the CIE System</i>. <a href="/wiki/Wiley_Interscience" title="Wiley Interscience" class="mw-redirect">Wiley Interscience</a>. p.&#160;37–46. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002%2F9780470175637.ch3" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002%2F9780470175637.ch3" rel="nofollow">10.1002/9780470175637.ch3</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780470049044" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-470-04904-4</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=3%3A+CIE+Colorimetry&amp;rft.atitle=Colorimetry%3A+Understanding+the+CIE+System&amp;rft.aulast=Schanda&amp;rft.aufirst=J%C3%A1nos&amp;rft.au=Schanda%2C+J%C3%A1nos&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.pages=p.%26nbsp%3B37%E2%80%9346&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BWiley+Interscience%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1002%2F9780470175637.ch3&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-470-04904-4&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Color_temperature"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-21"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMcCamy1992">McCamy, Calvin S. (April 1992). "Correlated color temperature as an explicit function of chromaticity coordinates". <i>Color Research &amp; Application</i> <b>17</b> (2): 142–144. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002%2Fcol.5080170211" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002%2Fcol.5080170211" rel="nofollow">10.1002/col.5080170211</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Correlated+color+temperature+as+an+explicit+function+of+chromaticity+coordinates&amp;rft.jtitle=Color+Research+%26+Application&amp;rft.aulast=McCamy&amp;rft.aufirst=Calvin+S.&amp;rft.au=McCamy%2C+Calvin+S.&amp;rft.date=April+1992&amp;rft.volume=17&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=142%E2%80%93144&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1002%2Fcol.5080170211&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Color_temperature"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> plus <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/col.5080180222" class="extiw" title="doi:10.1002/col.5080180222">erratum</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFHern.C3.A1ndez-Andr.C3.A9sLee.2C_Raymond_L..3B_Romero.2CJavier1999">Hernández-Andrés, Javier; Lee, Raymond L.; Romero,Javier (September 20 1999). "<a href="http://www.nadn.navy.mil/Users/oceano/raylee/papers/RLee_AO_CCTpaper.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.nadn.navy.mil/Users/oceano/raylee/papers/RLee_AO_CCTpaper.pdf" rel="nofollow">Calculating Correlated Color Temperatures Across the Entire Gamut of Daylight and Skylight Chromaticities</a>". <i>Applied Optics</i> <b>38</b> (27): 5703–5709. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1364%2FAO.38.005703" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1364%2FAO.38.005703" rel="nofollow">10.1364/AO.38.005703</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.nadn.navy.mil/Users/oceano/raylee/papers/RLee_AO_CCTpaper.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.nadn.navy.mil/Users/oceano/raylee/papers/RLee_AO_CCTpaper.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.nadn.navy.mil/Users/oceano/raylee/papers/RLee_AO_CCTpaper.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Calculating+Correlated+Color+Temperatures+Across+the+Entire+Gamut+of+Daylight+and+Skylight+Chromaticities&amp;rft.jtitle=Applied+Optics&amp;rft.aulast=Hern%C3%A1ndez-Andr%C3%A9s&amp;rft.aufirst=Javier&amp;rft.au=Hern%C3%A1ndez-Andr%C3%A9s%2C+Javier&amp;rft.au=Lee%2C+Raymond+L.%3B+Romero%2CJavier&amp;rft.date=September+20+1999&amp;rft.volume=38&amp;rft.issue=27&amp;rft.pages=5703%E2%80%935709&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1364%2FAO.38.005703&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nadn.navy.mil%2FUsers%2Foceano%2Fraylee%2Fpapers%2FRLee_AO_CCTpaper.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Color_temperature"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span><