<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> Gretag's <a href="http://www.xrite.com/documents/literature/gmb/en/200_spectrolino_manual_en.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.xrite.com/documents/literature/gmb/en/200_spectrolino_manual_en.pdf" rel="nofollow">SpectroLino</a> and X-Rite's <a href="http://www.pictureline.com/images/pdf/L11-246%20CM%20CompetitCompr_03-17-08.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.pictureline.com/images/pdf/L11-246%20CM%20CompetitCompr_03-17-08.pdf" rel="nofollow">ColorMunki</a> have an optical resolution of 10 nm.</li>
